<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= pageTitle %> - Medication Tracker
    </title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/Star_of_life2.svg.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100">
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

        <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-10 px-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Medication Tracker</h1>

                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
                    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg">
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
                            Medication Tracker was founded with a simple mission: to help people manage their
                            medications effectively and improve their health outcomes.
                        </p>

                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                            We believe that medication adherence shouldn't be complicated. Our platform provides simple
                            yet powerful tools to help you stay on track with your medications.
                        </p>

                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-gray-600">
                            <li>User-friendly interface designed for all ages</li>
                            <li>Secure and private health information management</li>
                            <li>Reliable reminder system</li>
                            <li>Comprehensive medication tracking</li>
                            <li>24/7 customer support</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
</body>

</html>